{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-129-repunit-divisibility","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 129: Deljenje repunita","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Broj koji se sastoji samo od jedne naziva se repunit. Definisaćemo $R(k)$ kao repunit dužine $k$; na primer, $R(6) = 111111$.</p>\n<p>Ako $n$ je pozitivan ceo broj i $GCD(n, 10) = 1$, može se pokazati da uvek postoji vrednost, $k$, takva da $R(k)$ je deljiv sa $n$, i neka je $A(n)$ najmanja vrednost $k$; na primer, $A(7) = 6$ i $A(41) = 5$.</p>\n<p>Najmanja vrednost $n$ za koju $A(n)$ počinje da prelazi deset je 17.</p>\n<p>Odredite najmanju vrednost $n$ koja uzrokuje da $A(n)$ počinje da prelazi milion.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3ef1000cf542c50ff01","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301756,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-129-repunit-divisibility"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function repunitDivisibility() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nrepunitDivisibility();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>repunitDivisibility()</code> treba vratiti <code>1000023</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repunitDivisibility(), 1000023);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-129-repunit-divisibility","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-eule